{
  "redirects": [
    {
      "source": "/",
      "has": [{ "type": "host", "value": "www.digitalprizebox.com" }],
      "destination": "https://digitalprizebox.com",
      "permanent": true
    },
    {
      "source": "/",
      "has": [{ "type": "host", "value": "app.digitalprizebox.com" }],
      "destination": "https://app.digitalprizebox.com/login",
      "permanent": false
    }
  ]
}
```

Commit it — Vercel picks up `vercel.json` automatically on the next deploy.

This tells Vercel:
```
www.digitalprizebox.com    → redirect to digitalprizebox.com (landing page)
app.digitalprizebox.com/   → redirect to /login (the app)
digitalprizebox.com        → serve normally (landing page for guests)
